'''本·普林頓'''（{{lang-en|'''Ben Purrington'''}}，{{bd|1996年|5月20日|catidx=Purrington, Ben}}）是英格蘭的職業足球運動員，司職左後衛，現效力於[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽]]中的[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查尔顿竞技]]。

==生涯==
出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[埃克塞特|埃克塞特]]，9歲加盟球會青年隊，2013年5月簽訂職業球員合約‧<ref>{{cite news|last=Metcalf|first=Rupert|title=Ben Purrington promoted to professional ranks by Plymouth Argyle|url=http://www.westernmorningnews.co.uk/Ben-Purrington-promoted-professional-ranks/story-19035780-detail/story.html|accessdate=26 December 2013|newspaper=Western Morning News|date=20 May 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227165022/http://www.westernmorningnews.co.uk/Ben-Purrington-promoted-professional-ranks/story-19035780-detail/story.html|archivedate=2013年12月27日|df=}}</ref>7個月後首次為球會上陣，<ref>{{cite news|last=Errington|first=Chris|title=Reuben Reid double inspires Argyle to dramatic win at Oxford|url=http://www.plymouthherald.co.uk/Reuben-Reid-double-inspires-Argyle-dramatic-win/story-20369112-detail/story.html|accessdate=26 December 2013|newspaper=Plymouth Herald|date=26 December 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227091752/http://www.plymouthherald.co.uk/Reuben-Reid-double-inspires-Argyle-dramatic-win/story-20369112-detail/story.html|archivedate=2013年12月27日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Errington|first=Chris|title=Teenage prospect Purrington enjoys his Argyle debut|url=http://www.plymouthherald.co.uk/Teenager-Purrington-enjoys-Plymouth-Argyle-debut/story-20372541-detail/story.html|accessdate=30 December 2013|newspaper=Plymouth Herald|date=27 December 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230111050/http://www.plymouthherald.co.uk/Teenager-Purrington-enjoys-Plymouth-Argyle-debut/story-20372541-detail/story.html|archivedate=2013年12月30日}}</ref> 在第四次出場時，[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]對戰[[維爾港足球會|維爾港]]的比賽射入首個入球。<ref>{{cite news|last=Errington|first=Chris|title=Port Vale 2 Plymouth Argyle 2: Match report|url=http://www.plymouthherald.co.uk/Port-Vale-2-Plymouth-Argyle-2-Match-report/story-20402398-detail/story.html|accessdate=5 January 2014|newspaper=Plymouth Herald|date=5 January 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/2014010604082